== 创作 ==
2008年7月28日开拍。拍摄地有[[德里|德里]]、[[班加罗尔|班加罗尔]]、[[孟买|孟买]]、[[拉達克|拉達克]]、Chail和[[西姆拉|西姆拉]]。Aamir等几位主演于2008年9月上旬进剧组，于同年12月完成拍摄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiafm.com/news/2008/07/28/11730/index.html |title=Rajkumar Hirani's 3 Idiots goes on floors |publisher=indiafm.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080804233117/http://www.indiafm.com/news/2008/07/28/11730/index.html |archivedate=2008-08-04 |accessdate=2011-12-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ia.rediff.com/movies/2008/aug/28look1.htm |title=Shooting for 3 Idiots underway |publisher=rediff.com |access-date=2011-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614061521/http://ia.rediff.com/movies/2008/aug/28look1.htm |archive-date=2012-06-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主要拍摄场地有[[印度管理研究所邦加羅爾分校|印度管理研究所邦加羅爾分校]]，剧组在此花了33天<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/uncategorized/shooting-three-idiots-is-like-holidaying-for-aamir-khan_100143291.html |title=Shooting ‘Three Idiots’ is like holidaying |publisher=thaindian.com |access-date=2011-12-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AibQ0W4z?url=http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/uncategorized/shooting-three-idiots-is-like-holidaying-for-aamir-khan_100143291.html |archive-date=2012-09-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。其中有一幕在[[印度理工學院|印度理工學院]]孟買校區拍摄。

